subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: People do not ask Cale Yarborough about his titles in 1976, ’77 and ’78 as much as they ask him to recall a fistfight at the ’79 Daytona 500.
